README for squirrelmail-translations

REQUIREMENTS

PRE-INSTALL
Export variable containing locales of choice (otherwice all locales will be
installed), and htdocs root directory (I prefer srv/www/apache/htdocs):

 export SQM_LANG="ru_RU it_IT"
 export SQM_HTDOCS_ROOT="srv/www/apache/htdocs"

It will be used inside Pkgfile, so do not wonder if footprint will give you
an error.

